snippet: Florida officials said they had forwarded complaints about alleged voter registration fraud against the state Democratic Party and two other groups to the Florida Department of Law Enforcement.
abstract: Florida officials say they have forwarded complaints about alleged voter registration fraud against state Democratic Party and two other groups to Florida's Department of Law Enforcement.
lead_paragraph: Florida officials said they had forwarded complaints about alleged voter registration fraud against the state Democratic Party and two other groups to the Florida Department of Law Enforcement.
